com.ulflander.minethat.job
Class Job

java.lang.Object
  com.ulflander.minethat.job.Job
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Job
extends Object
implements Serializable

A job holds information about documents to be processed, processors to run on them or presets of processors to use, and also about the customer that initiated the job.
